		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Velorian&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I am currently a level 42 bard. I am stuck on which song to chose, i have been using them in groups for a while now, well since i got them both, and i always which one i should use, they cancel each other out which is a pain. I was wondering which i should use, or should i just base it on the circumstance? the two songs are psalm of vitality, and the other is psalm of mystic shielding, one gives magic protection, health regen and absorb magic damage, and small amout of ac, and the other gievs a ds, poison resistand armor class, any help would be appriciated</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from England</td><td align="right" id="fs8" >1 Replies</td></tr></table>
