		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=247125"><span id=Scholar>Jiggidyjay of the Seven Seas</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br /><img alt="Avatar" height="73" width="100" src="/uf/Jiggidyjay/Avatar2.jpg"><br /><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*"/><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />1475 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.56]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Jiggidyjay&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>Psalm of mystic shielding will probably be more useful in most situations. Just remember that the absorb damage component is kind of like a rune, so if you're tank is getting nuked a lot, the song is going to keep dropping.<br><br>Another thing to look at is the DS from your other psalms. It's not huge, but it is modded by voice, so if you wanted to amp it once in a while, it could be nice, especially since slowing at that level really isn't that effective.<br><br>So, if you want the extra HP regen and MR, go with shielding. If you want a specific resist and a stacking DS, go with one of the elemental/disease/poison psalms. It's going to depend on your group and situation more then anything.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006062" target="akztarg">Jiggidyjay</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Ranger</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1003866" target="akztarg">Zingin Ansinging</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Bard of <a href="HTTP://firestormers.com/viewnews.php" target="akztarg">The Firestormers</a></span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006061" target="akztarg">Zolotaya</a> - <span class="sm">Ms Necro</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1189723" target="akztarg">Zeibis</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Monk</span class="sm"></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from the 